VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and decides to go scorched earth on you. So there are of course a couple of options out there already. You could carry around a little pocket fan like this, which is very bulky, very noisy,'

[00:31] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and definitely not &gt;&gt; [music] &gt;&gt; discreet. I\'ve also seen small fans like this with a neck band that kind of rest around your neck and blow cold air at your face. Once again, those are not very discreet and they\'re not very'

[00:44] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'stylish and they\'re also quite noisy. And that is where products like this from Sony come into play. This might just be the world\'s greatest ever personal air conditioning unit. The'

[00:57] [scene:talk]
